directions: Stir chili with beans and corn together in a large skillet over medium heat; cook until heated through, about 5 minutes.
Break eggs onto chili mixture and top eggs with American cheese.
Cover skillet and cook until eggs are set and cheese is melted, about 10 minutes.
ingredients: 3 slices American Cheese, cut diagonally into halves
title: Skillet Chili 'N Eggs
